components.name: Studio
components.description: Please enter tickets related to Titanium Studio here.

fields.description:
Steps:
(1) Upgrade or Reinstall with Titanium Studio 3.3.0.201407100905
(2) Create Alloy project with "Default Alloy Project"
(3) Build and Run when target to HTC one 801e m7 device / Emulator with Android 4.4.2, SDK level 19
(4) Result as attachment "build error msg.txt"

If use the Titanium Terminal and type "ti info", similar error message occur as attachment "ti info.txt"
fields.summary: Titanium 3.3.0.GA bug when build and/or just ti info
fields.environment: OS: Window 8.0 64bit, Titanium Studio 3.3.0.201407100905, Titanium SDK 3.3.0.GA, Java 1.7

comments.body:
More detail and correction:
(1) JDK = 1.7.0_40
(2) Building App working ok if switch to Titanium SDK 3.2.3.GA

Hello!

Can you please provide the logs from Ti Studio? 

1. Open Studio
2. Go to help menu
3. Click on Studio
4. View log

Share the log here, please. 

Best Regards,
Mauro

Log as following:
